data.description: This custom built mid century home offers unique features throughout. With custom birch built -in cabinetry in the master bedroom, European pergo in the family and dining rooms and an additional kitchenette for your entertaining pleasure. Three generous sized bedrooms with a fourth bdrm/office. Masterbedrm with beamed catherdral ceiling, vanity area, walk-in closet and bathrm. Birch cabinetry, breakfast bar and charming eat-in area with cathedral ceiling in the kitchen. Beautiful hardwood flooring. 3 fireplaces. Deck and patio plus garden shed complete your beautiful outdoor setting. Home warranty included...Great location with access to enjoy Rockfords best. Near Sinnissppi Golf Course/ Park, Andersons Japanese Garden, University of Illinois School of Medicine, Keith Country Day Private school and so close to the Rockford River District. Nestled in a beautiful setting with addtl wooded lot full of possibilities. A wonderful place to call home. A must see! Click the virtual tour above.
